1
00:00:57,360 --> 00:01:00,960
At first, I thought Du Long was with you

2
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:04,880
Now it seems he was part of your plan too

3
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:09,400
Du Long is not left-handed

4
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:12,840
But the pen for his note was on the left side

5
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:15,920
He did not write the suicide note

6
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:18,720
You really are observant

7
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:21,440
You were not born left-handed either

8
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:23,320
You use your left hand

9
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:25,440
Because you do not have a right hand

10
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:29,800
Impressive. I was right about you

11
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:38,560
Since you have seen my hand

12
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:41,960
I should keep my promise and marry you

13
00:01:42,960 --> 00:01:43,760
Master Ai

14
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:44,960
Ah, no

15
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:47,200
I should call you

16
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:48,280
Wang

17
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,440
Yue

18
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:50,360
ya

19
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:55,160
The hand bone in the box

20
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:57,200
Belongs to an adult woman

21
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:59,200
And the right hand bone beside it

22
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:00,840
Judging by its bone age

23
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,840
Should belong to a 13-year-old girl

24
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:06,600
The Wang Family used your right hand bone

25
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:08,000
You hate the Wang Family

26
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:10,000
So you planned all of this

27
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:14,040
That's right. The Wang Family all deserve to die

28
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,720
I understand why you hate the Wang Family

29
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:19,520
But why did you harm the Lu Family

30
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,920
The Lu Family deserve to die too

31
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:26,040
Just finding any right hand would not work

32
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:28,840
Blood ties are connected

33
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:31,680
It should fool ghosts and gods more easily

34
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:35,920
Better to use the hand of close kin

35
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:41,720
Men, seize her

36
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:46,240
My only regret is not killing the Lu matriarch myself

37
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:47,920
Do you know

38
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,240
When Qingyi came to see me

39
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,360
Her face was covered in bruises

40
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:55,560
You do not want to live so miserably, do you

41
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:57,480
I can help you

42
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,560
This is Soul-Bewitching Herb

43
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,080
Take it

44
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:07,960
Soul-Bewitching Herb

45
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:11,160
The Lu matriarch wronged you

46
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,680
But what about the others

47
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,480
Why did you harm them

48
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:19,400
You really are only fit to deal with bones

49
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,520
What do you mean

50
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:24,160
You understand human nature too little

51
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,840
Perhaps you do not know

52
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:27,440
Zhao Xunan's elder sister

53
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:30,920
Was forced to her death by the Lu heir himself

54
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,480
Let me go

55
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:38,000
For the sake of me saving your brother

56
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:38,880
What

57
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:42,360
Do you want to hear Xiao Shen's story too

58
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:44,880
His real name was Li Changsheng

59
00:03:44,920 --> 00:03:47,080
Yet he never dared say his own name

60
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:50,520
Mayor, they kept secretly selling girls to the Wang Family

61
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:52,120
But they made Li Zhong the scapegoat

62
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,880
After Xiao Shen's father was murdered

63
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,600
He was forced into homelessness

64
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:56,680
And suffered endless abuse

65
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:57,960
Was he not innocent

66
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:00,520
Everyone he killed deserved to die

67
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:02,920
Master Ai

68
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:05,280
I want to find a good burial site

69
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,680
For one whose bones are gone

70
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:09,160
One whose bones are gone

71
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,040
You mean a cenotaph

72
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,440
My father's remains are gone

73
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,880
We can only use his clothes in place of him

74
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:18,240
Have you suffered some grave injustice

75
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,640
Then let those villains

76
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:28,640
Taste the torment of burning flames too

77
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,080
Even if you've been wronged

78
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:37,600
there is justice and the law

79
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:40,600
why did you take lives on your own?

80
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:45,360
Justice and the law?

81
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:48,360
The Wang Family, Lu Family, the mayor

82
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:50,280
these people rule Nanwan Town

83
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,240
and do every kind of evil

84
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:52,880
What damn law is there?

85
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,760
We shouldn't take lives on our own

86
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,800
Whose life isn't a life?

87
00:04:58,280 --> 00:05:00,760
Are the lives of nobodies like us,

88
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:01,760
with no power or influence, not lives?

89
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:03,760
Was my mother's life not a life too?

90
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:05,600
Are we supposed to suffer humiliation

91
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,120
and just deserve to die?

92
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:10,280
Yueya, calm down first

93
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:11,840
I can help you

94
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:13,120
If the town won't handle it,

95
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,080
we can gather evidence

96
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:15,480
We can... No need

97
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:18,840
I'll make them pay with my own way

98
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:22,840
The Fifth Concubine is key to my revenge

99
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,080
Brother Zheng Yu

100
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,480
I'm sorry

101
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:28,840
Xunan is completely innocent

102
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:29,920
Don't hurt her

103
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,240
Keep a close watch on him

104
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,320
Wang Yueya

105
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,600
Master

106
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:59,600
Master, you're still alive

107
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,760
I always thought you had already...

108
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:04,880
Stay out of what happens next

109
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,760
Why are you helping Wang Yueya?

110
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:14,200
Because all of this started with me

111
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:16,280
I am the real sinner

112
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:18,720
What are you saying?

113
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:22,800
Yueya is actually my granddaughter

114
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:27,440
Back then, I loved a woman dearly

115
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:30,160
Just because I was a Bone Collector,

116
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:33,560
her family forcibly tore us apart

117
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:38,200
I truly didn't know she was pregnant

118
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:42,120
So Miss Shuang'er is your daughter?

119
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:46,120
Ever since Shuang'er married into the Wang Family,

120
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,640
the Wang Family kept targeting her

121
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:52,040
and spread rumors she was immoral

122
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:53,880
and that was why Wang Sanming killed her

123
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,960
Only later did I learn

124
00:06:56,560 --> 00:07:00,520
the Wang Family fed her alive to that jerk

125
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,080
That means

126
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:07,000
Wang Shengchang has lied all along

127
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,720
And not only that

128
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:11,360
they even wanted Yueya dead

129
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:15,520
After the Bone gathering ritual that year,

130
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:17,720
my conscience never let me rest

131
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:21,440
so I found the child whose right hand was cut off

132
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:23,280
but on her

133
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:27,040
I saw the token I gave my beloved back then

134
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:30,800
only then did I know she was my granddaughter

135
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,480
But I never expected

136
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:40,120
that was where Wang Shengchang kept that jerk

137
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:43,920
He meant to leave Yueya there to live or die

138
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:50,840
I lost one arm

139
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:53,640
I suppose it was retribution

140
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:55,240
What exactly is that monster?

141
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:59,680
He is the son of Wang Shengchang and Madam Wang

142
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,720
Wang Shengchang's son?

143
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:04,840
Yes. He was deformed from birth

144
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:06,320
with a grotesque appearance

145
00:08:06,760 --> 00:08:08,480
and white hair all over his body

146
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:11,720
He liked eating raw meat since childhood

147
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:15,080
At first, they fed him poultry

148
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:18,480
Later, they even used living people

149
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:21,920
The bones you saw at the mass grave

150
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:25,880
belong to Nanwan Town's countless wronged dead

151
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,160
Besides that

152
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:31,720
his concubines would also have blood drawn

153
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,680
to feed that jerk

154
00:08:34,040 --> 00:08:37,440
and end up as offerings on ritual day

155
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,320
Why did they perform sacrifices?

156
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:43,200
Just for a lie

157
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:46,720
Even now, Wang Shengchang still doesn't know

158
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:50,080
he killed so many people for the sacrifice

159
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,360
in the end,

160
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,440
it was all fake
